text.section:
The SHOP Exchange shall be designed to balance:
the viability of the SHOP Exchange as an alternative for qualified employers and their employees who have not been able historically to access and afford insurance in the small group market;
the need for stability and predictability in employers' health insurance costs incurred on behalf of their employees;
the desirability of providing employees with a meaningful choice among high-quality and affordable health benefit plans; and
the need to facilitate continuity of care for employees who change employers or health benefit plans.
